  "instructions": [
    "Cook bigoli in boiling salted water until al dente, about 8 minutes.",
    "Drain and set aside.",
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add sliced onions and cook, stirring occasionally, until caramelized and golden brown, about 25 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in red wine vinegar and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Season with salt, black pepper, and sumac.",
    "Toss cooked bigoli with the onion mixture and transfer to a serving dish.",
    "Sprinkle with grated Parmesan cheese and chopped parsley.",
    "Drizzle with lemon juice and serve hot.",
    "Finish with a sprinkle of sumac for garnish.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
